title: The default value set in list box of report parameter is lost after modifying the default value
description: Description: When modifying the default value set in a list box of a report parameter, the default value is lost. Steps to reproduce: 1.
OB: The default value set in the list box of the report parameter is being lost after modifying the default value.
EB: The default value set in the list box of the report parameter should be retained after modifying the default value.
SR: Ensure that the default value set in the list box of the report parameter is not lost when modifying the default value.
